# aws-clipboard-login — account → profile/region mapping
#
# One entry per line:
#   ACCOUNT_ID  PROFILE_NAME  REGION
#
# Accounts that aren't listed here still work — they're registered under a
# profile named after the account ID, in the default region (us-east-1 unless
# AWS_CLIPBOARD_DEFAULT_REGION is set).
#
# Examples (uncomment and edit):
# 123456789012  dev    us-east-1
# 210987654321  prod   eu-west-1
